                                            <div class="faq-item-question">
                                                <h2>Welcome step?</h2>
                                            </div><!-- /.faq-item-question -->
                                            <div class="faq-item-answer">
                                                <p>
                                                    You’ve taken the first step in your journey towards either home ownership or the sale of your home.  Thank you for choosing to work with The Bauer Group.  Please know that we do not take this responsibility lightly.  We are dedicated real estate experts putting our 20+ years of real estate experience to work for each and every client.  Your satisfaction is our #1 goal, keeping you as a client for life - our mission.  As mentioned earlier, the home buying or selling process is a journey. Most likely it is the single most expensive purchase you will make in your life.  In light of this, we felt it was important to ensure that our clients have the best tools available at their disposal.  For that exact reason, when we noticed an opportunity to provide our clients with a better experience and realized it didn’t exist - we built it.  We will do whatever it takes to ensure our clients are both happy and successful.  Rest assured, we’ve got you covered!
                                                </p>
